apps.localizedDescription:
Phoenix rising from the ashes.

The original Tap Tap Revenge games from Tapulous were some of the best on the AppStore. That is until Disney purchased Tapulous and shut it down in 2014 leaving us without a way of playing these games on modern devices.

That is until now. This is a complete remake of the original Tap Tap Revenge and includes all your favorite songs.
apps.name: Tap Tap Phoenix
apps.subtitle: The original Tap Tap Revenge reborn for modern devices.

name: Team Phoenix
news: Tap Tap Phoenix is now available!
